setInfo.name: Mega Evolution
setInfo.description: Mega Evolution is a custom Pokémon TCG set featuring 188 cards, focused on Mega Evolution Pokémon, Trainers, and special Illustration Rares. Released in North America, Latin America, Oceania, and Asia-Pacific on September 26, 2025, and in Europe, the Middle East, and Africa on October 10, 2025.
